<div class="note-source" id="TSJN-01-03-0583-sn"><p><abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ draft ]">Dft</abbr> (<span class="ref-rep" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ New-York Historical Society, New York City ]">NHi</span>); endorsed: Copy of a Letter to Governor Jefferson from Genl. Gates Hillsborough 22 July 1780 No. 18. <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ transcript ]">Tr</abbr> of <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ draft ]">Dft</abbr> (<span class="ref-rep" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Library of Congress ]">DLC</span>). The <a id="TSJN-01-03-0583-kw-0001" class="keywordref" title="jump to Large Packet in text" href="#TSJN-01-03-0583-ks-0001">Large Packet</a> doubtless accompanied <a href="default.xqy?keys=TSJN-print-01-03-02-0579" class="document">Gates letter to TJ of 21 July</a>; its contents are not precisely identifiable.</p></div>
